          <text>
                    <body>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>July 6, 1851</date>.</p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">In haste I take<lb/> my pen to inform you that
                                                  <persName>Mr. H. L. Moss</persName><lb/> at
                                                  <placeName>Dayton Ohio</placeName> wishes to be a
                                        subscriber for your<lb/> Occident commencing with the
                                                  <date>June</date> No. of this<lb/> year. Please
                                        send it to him.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I do not yet know whether I can get
                                        subscribers<lb/> enough to sustain the Shulamite, but if I
                                        do, it may<lb/> be commenced soon. If you have time to drop
                                        me a<lb/> few lines, I wish you would give me your
                                        opinion<lb/> on the subject and whether you think it will
                                        meet<lb/> with favor in your region. If it go on it will
                                        cer=<lb/>tainly be what it proposes to be—a paper open to
                                        Jews<lb/> as well as Christians—a paper in which Judaism
                                        may<lb/> be defended and advanced, though it will
                                        circulate<lb/> much more among Christians, than
                                        Jews—probably five times<lb/> as much. I would be glad to
                                        have your <hi rend="underline">private</hi> opinion.<lb/> I
                                        do not wish any public notice. Address me <placeName>95
                                                  Greene Street</placeName>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(7)">Yours most respectfully</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName role="author">M. R. Miller</persName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
